<plot>Italy, 1757. Meek tailor Pippo Popolino disguises himself as the great Casanova in order to romance attractive widow Francesca. He little suspects what he's getting into: locked into the incongruous role by the greed of the real Casanova's creditors, Pippo must journey to Venice on a delicate mission far beyond his capabilities...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?095754</url></doc>
